Hi Does anyone know if its possible to group by month and year in hubdb i have seen that this is possible in jinja is it possible to replicate in hubl
```{% for year, year_group in EventsList|groupby('date.year') %}
    {% for month, list in year_group|groupby('date.month') %}
        &lt;b&gt;{{ month }} {{ year }}&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
        {% for event in list %}
            &lt;i&gt;{{event.title}}&lt;/i&gt;
        {% endfor %}
    {% endfor %}
{% endfor %}```
